{"title":"乡村春节","authors":["商泽军"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":2,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村春节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"商泽军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是嫁姑娘的时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙头红盖住了乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖住了父母的脸庞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们扯住新娘的衣角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是拽住春天的尾巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“捉到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捉到了”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节是孩子们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最好有雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那白的音乐在瓦上演奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的春联与孩子们的脸红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相映"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们拍着手掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和雪人一块唱歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗跑过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸭跑过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们听不懂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和雪人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱了些什么歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节是属于回忆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人们开始说起往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸的皱纹里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是风霜也是财富"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛老了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那挂在墙上的农具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也老了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一领蓑衣也挂墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那上面贴了一个“喜”字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像春天也穿着蓑衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该回乡的回乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个老人站在村口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后的一棵榆树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他的象征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是他儿子回家的理由"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人站着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自言自语——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说火车提速了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子的脚步也提速了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但还是不见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那路途上熟悉的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒是春节酿出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆竹是春节炸响的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果说春节是有音符的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是炒菜的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与温情的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果说春节是用脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走着来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那春节的脚长在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获物身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长在新鲜的衣服上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节披着新衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿着新鞋来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节要人们给她一枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压岁钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节要人们从她这里购买"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红的喜庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和年夜欢乐的心情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节是圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她和大家坐在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围着肉馅和素馅饺子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节是有姓名的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你找不到她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说不出她姓赵还是姓李"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们知道乡村春节的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她叫欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}